ecent efforts toward high-throughput calculations of\ncarrier transport. In the last part, we discuss the extension of the\nmethodology to study spintronics and topological materials and we comment on\nthe possibility of incorporating Berry-phase effects and many-body correlations\nbeyond the standard Boltzmann formalism.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Aug 2019 17:16:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-19"}
