ng\nCharon ejects only much smaller particles, however, graze-and-merge impacts are\na plausible formation channel for the Pluto-Charon binary and an ensemble of\nsmall, circumbinary satellites.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Aug 2019 18:00:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-02"}
