ufficient\nto model Sgr A* at high flux levels and should be updated. Potential physical\norigins of Sgr A*'s unprecedented brightness may be from changes in the\naccretion-flow as a result of the star S0-2's closest passage to the black hole\nin 2018 or from a delayed reaction to the approach of the dusty object G2 in\n2014. Additional multi-wavelength observations will be necessary to both\nmonitor Sgr A* for potential state changes and to constrain the physical\nprocesses responsible for its current variability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Aug 2019 18:00:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-02"}
