l functionality and the muon detector efficiency to be kept close to\n100%. The possibility of making the recovery faster and even more effective by\nadding a small percentage of oxygen in the gas mixture has been studied and\nsuccessfully tested.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Aug 2019 14:23:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 20 May 2021 08:17:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-21"}
